                },
                {
                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                    "id": "310aea7d-0348-4cb9-912d-08f469528fdb",
                    "actorId": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                    "actorId2": "d790a30c-ba0a-45af-94dc-c5066fcb20a4",
                    "text": "Hi, thanks for returning all the stuff. I hope you like the apples I left for you.",
                    "emotion": "0",
                    "emotion2": "0",
                    "device": "0",
                    "device2": "0"
                },
                {
                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                    "id": "ddfc3647-b20b-4d6d-9584-b940e0988e2f",
                    "actorId": "d790a30c-ba0a-45af-94dc-c5066fcb20a4",
                    "actorId2": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                    "text": "<sniff> The apples... yes... the only joy I have left in life since meeting you.",
                    "emotion": "2",
                    "emotion2": "4",
                    "device": "0",
                    "device2": "0"
                },
                {
                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                    "id": "c2cbbf2c-d41f-4665-bfbb-a76c80e1ab6c",
                    "actorId": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                    "actorId2": "d790a30c-ba0a-45af-94dc-c5066fcb20a4",
                    "text": "What's wrong?",
                    "emotion": "0",
                    "emotion2": "2",
                    "device": "0",
                    "device2": "0"
                },
                {
                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                    "id": "537cb4aa-9a50-4265-8746-7c3a24dcfc5b",
                    "actorId": "d790a30c-ba0a-45af-94dc-c5066fcb20a4",
                    "actorId2": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                    "text": "After I had to return all the things I found, I was demoted from Finder. Now I'm only a lowly Seeker. The Castle Kwirks blamed me for getting caught.",
                    "emotion": "2",
                    "emotion2": "0",
                    "device": "0",
                    "device2": "0"
                },
                {
                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                    "id": "d09b2430-84a4-430b-aa55-b76bce1b8a47",
                    "actorId": "d790a30c-ba0a-45af-94dc-c5066fcb20a4",
                    "actorId2": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                    "text": "So now, all I have to look forward to is the occasional apple.",
                    "emotion": "2",
                    "emotion2": "0",
                    "device": "0",
                    "device2": "0"
                },
                {
                    "type": "nodes.showMenu",
                    "id": "bcd27e75-9e7f-4468-bd9f-39aa262a8417",
                    "options": [
                        {
                            "type": "options.text",
                            "id": "0a4dcc64-94f1-45d8-bc10-374ec655cc83",
                            "text": "Ask About the Apple Core",
                            "nodes": [
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "79834180-85b8-477a-a5db-602ab1e62d7d",
                                    "actorId": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "actorId2": "d790a30c-ba0a-45af-94dc-c5066fcb20a4",
                                    "text": "So did you leave an apple core in my room for a reason?",
                                    "emotion": "0",
                                    "emotion2": "0",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "658731cc-8fe4-4a95-8b01-51b354b120c8",
                                    "actorId": "d790a30c-ba0a-45af-94dc-c5066fcb20a4",
                                    "actorId2": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "text": "Yes, I'm down to my last apple or two. The Kwirk King said we can't <i>Find</i> things from the school since I got caught. ",
                                    "emotion": "0",
                                    "emotion2": "0",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "8cb5e594-09f0-44cc-affe-9f0c02997fd1",
                                    "actorId": "d790a30c-ba0a-45af-94dc-c5066fcb20a4",
                                    "actorId2": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "text": "So the only apples I can get are the ones you give me. I thought you'd like to know that.",
                                    "emotion": "2",
                                    "emotion2": "0",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                }
                            ],
                            "expression": {
                                "type": "expressions.inTags",
                                "scope": "scene",
                                "scopeId": "9897ecb3-4200-4884-867a-2840471747b8",
                                "scopeFilterId": null,
                                "tags": "AppleCore1found",
                                "has": true
                            },
                            "ignoreChildAvailability": false,
                            "minutes": "4",
                            "ExitMenu": false
                        },
                        {
                            "type": "options.text",
                            "id": "02bcceb6-374a-421f-8779-4d55d62a1d12",
                            "text": "Ask About Kwirks",
                            "nodes": [
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "14c6759f-7b9c-42cc-baf2-89a127d47bc8",
                                    "actorId": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "actorId2": "d790a30c-ba0a-45af-94dc-c5066fcb20a4",
                                    "text": "Okay, so what are you? Where do you live? How do you get around the castle?",
                                    "emotion": "0",
                                    "emotion2": "0",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "f1e498f2-e960-4f26-8a8e-8e8e7ff352ec",
                                    "actorId": "d790a30c-ba0a-45af-94dc-c5066fcb20a4",
                                    "actorId2": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "text": "I'm a Castle Kwirk, of course. We live in the castle. This castle is huge, and we know where to hide so nobody can find us.",
                                    "emotion": "0",
                                    "emotion2": "0",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.showMenu",
                                    "id": "e8aea8d1-b7b8-4a46-badd-c05261253211",
                                    "options": [
                                        {
                                            "type": "options.text",
                                            "id": "3423954c-a667-4bb9-b883-d960d9de0e98",
                                            "text": "Ask About Castle Kwirks",
                                            "nodes": [
                                                {
                                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                                    "id": "a880d7c4-b85f-47a8-aa1e-7f982df155c9",
                                                    "actorId": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                                    "actorId2": "d790a30c-ba0a-45af-94dc-c5066fcb20a4",
                                                    "text": "How long have Kwirks lived in this castle? I never heard of Kwirks before I came here.",
                                                    "emotion": "0",
                                                    "emotion2": "0",
                                                    "device": "0",
                                                    "device2": "0"
                                                },
                                                {
                                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                                    "id": "8e1ae3ba-75a1-4c41-8568-d35e03c7c670",
                                                    "actorId": "d790a30c-ba0a-45af-94dc-c5066fcb20a4",
                                                    "actorId2": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                                    "text": "We Kwirks have been here forever! Well, maybe not that long. My great-great grand Kwirk came here.",
                                                    "emotion": "0",
                                                    "emotion2": "0",
                                                    "device": "0",
                                                    "device2": "0"
                                                }
                                            ],
                                            "expression": null,
                                            "ignoreChildAvailability": false,
                                            "minutes": "3",
                                            "ExitMenu": false
                                        },
                                        {
                                            "type": "options.text",
                                            "id": "89a3da4f-6c3c-4626-a591-407f8fa56b38",
                                            "text": "Ask About Castle History",
                                            "nodes": [
                                                {
                                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                                    "id": "1402bd18-2a3c-4a45-93d4-49e592bc923d",
                                                    "actorId": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                                    "actorId2": "d790a30c-ba0a-45af-94dc-c5066fcb20a4",
                                                    "text": "You must know a lot about what happened before the school came here. Who was around here then?",
                                                    "emotion": "0",
                                                    "emotion2": "0",
                                                    "device": "0",
                                                    "device2": "0"
                                                },
                                                {
                                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                                    "id": "e1163dc2-68fe-443c-9d2b-9be2bc3da5d4",
                                                    "actorId": "d790a30c-ba0a-45af-94dc-c5066fcb20a4",
                                                    "actorId2": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                                    "text": "Before the school moved in, there were just three guys - the Librarian, the Guardian, and the Creepy Guy.",
                                                    "emotion": "0",
                                                    "emotion2": "0",
                                                    "device": "0",
                                                    "device2": "0"
                                                },
                                                {
                                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                                    "id": "494baf2b-9b56-4486-b79e-65d6fd642106",
                                                    "actorId": "d790a30c-ba0a-45af-94dc-c5066fcb20a4",
                                                    "actorId2": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                                    "text": "One day, this new guy came to the castle to talk to the others. He looked a lot like that painting of the dying guy up in the room with the statue of the boy and the sea serpent. But that painting came later.",
                                                    "emotion": "0",
                                                    "emotion2": "0",
                                                    "device": "0",
                                                    "device2": "0"
                                                },
                                                {
                                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                                    "id": "09d325fd-0d52-4784-9d66-d3bf00c8c99e",
                                                    "actorId": "d790a30c-ba0a-45af-94dc-c5066fcb20a4",
                                                    "actorId2": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                                    "text": "So the new guy speaks with the Guardian and the Librarian, but not the Creepy Guy. Nobody talks to the Creepy Guy. Then the Guardian and the new guy leaves and never comes back.",
                                                    "emotion": "0",
                                                    "emotion2": "0",
                                                    "device": "0",
                                                    "device2": "0"
                                                },
                                                {
                                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                                    "id": "324918ff-e969-48e7-ad52-011d1561758e",
                                                    "actorId": "d790a30c-ba0a-45af-94dc-c5066fcb20a4",
                                                    "actorId2": null,
                                                    "text": "And then, there's a bunch of guys like knights and stuff who come here to talk to the Librarian. They have a big argument and after that, the school sets up here.",
                                                    "emotion": "0",
                                                    "emotion2": "0",
                                                    "device": "0",
                                                    "device2": "0"
                                                },
                                                {
                                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                                    "id": "de0f7282-1bef-4f43-a7a8-eb12d3c7a069",
                                                    "actorId": "d790a30c-ba0a-45af-94dc-c5066fcb20a4",
                                                    "actorId2": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                                    "text": "And that's all I know.",
                                                    "emotion": "0",
                                                    "emotion2": "0",
                                                    "device": "0",
                                                    "device2": "0"
                                                }
                                            ],
                                            "expression": null,
                                            "ignoreChildAvailability": false,
                                            "minutes": "10",
                                            "ExitMenu": false
                                        },
                                        {
                                            "type": "options.text",
                                            "id": "63cb5f0f-9a8e-4939-a900-fb297d70c94f",
                                            "text": "Ask About Secret Passages",
                                            "nodes": [
                                                {
                                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                                    "id": "d7ccd06b-c76f-42db-bd7c-906655514cfc",
                                                    "actorId": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                                    "actorId2": "d790a30c-ba0a-45af-94dc-c5066fcb20a4",
                                                    "text": "So what other secret passages do you know about besides the dark one?",
                                                    "emotion": "0",
                                                    "emotion2": "0",
                                                    "device": "0",
                                                    "device2": "0"
                                                },
                                                {
                                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                                    "id": "af2f95ff-3081-4ce9-be2b-122cec660fed",
                                                    "actorId": "d790a30c-ba0a-45af-94dc-c5066fcb20a4",
                                                    "actorId2": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                                    "text": "Depends upon what you call a secret... All the Kwirks know about them. But there's one down from the dark one with crypts and stuff. It's got doors that Kwirks can't open. Guess they got to be opened from the other side first.",
                                                    "emotion": "0",
                                                    "emotion2": "0",
                                                    "device": "0",
                                                    "device2": "0"
                                                },
                                                {
                                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                                    "id": "cdcf6821-1cae-4d38-af6c-7f8c030101e2",
                                                    "actorId": "d790a30c-ba0a-45af-94dc-c5066fcb20a4",
                                                    "actorId2": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                                    "text": "There's a whole dungeon area in the castle that no Kwirk goes to anymore... the Wine Cellar is too full of Drats now. ",
                                                    "emotion": "0",
                                                    "emotion2": "0",
                                                    "device": "0",
                                                    "device2": "0"
                                                },
                                                {
                                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                                    "id": "83bcaaae-5c2e-43db-a349-1d933c49672f",
                                                    "actorId": "d790a30c-ba0a-45af-94dc-c5066fcb20a4",
                                                    "actorId2": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                                    "text": "Ugh, Drats. Nasty things. We warn the baby Kwirks that the Drats will get them if they aren't good. We warn everyone else that the Drats will get them if they aren't fast. ",
                                                    "emotion": "3",
                                                    "emotion2": "0",
                                                    "device": "0",
                                                    "device2": "0"
                                                }
                                            ],
                                            "expression": null,
                                            "ignoreChildAvailability": false,
                                            "minutes": "6",
                                            "ExitMenu": false
                                        }
                                    ],
                                    "AutoAddDone": true,
                                    "Unique": false
                                }
                            ],
                            "expression": null,
                            "ignoreChildAvailability": false,
                            "minutes": "3",
                            "ExitMenu": false
                        },
                        {
